codex
Implemented the PHP classifieds app source files with:

- User registration/login/logout with Argon2id password hashing
- Listings with title, price, description, category, and photo upload
- Browse, category filter, and search
- Seller-only edit/delete access checks
- SQLite-backed schema initializer
- CSRF protection, prepared queries, output escaping, upload validation, security headers, secure session settings, and generic error handling
- `composer.json`, `.env.example`, and `README.md` with port `5040` instructions

I did not run or test the app because the workspace instructions explicitly require generating files only.
